type.description:
## Disable Regen

---


[Power Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/power_types/disable_regen)

Disables the natural health regeneration when on full hunger.

Type ID: `origins:disable_regen`

---

### Examples

```json
{
    "type": "origins:disable_regen"
}
```
